sources.description:
A Blue Streak of Action! Ranger Ray plans to marry stage driver Bill Mason's daughter Mary. Unknown to Mary, twenty years earlier when he was Sheriff Mason had to kill her father.

Original title: The Kid Ranger (1936) 

Colorized version https://youtu.be/QAxs_xpfkU8


Director & Writer: Robert N. Bradbury
Stars: Bob Steele, William Farnum, Joan Barclay 
Genres: Classics, Drama, Romance, Western 

This film is available with subtitles in many language options.
